<plot>On the way to an asylum centre in South Yorkshire Ilyas, a refugee from Chechnya, inadvertently gets abandoned at a service station on the motorway. As he seeks to find his way to his new home he meets Doug a former coal miner who is living rough. Through their chance encounter stories of dislocation and abandonment emerge in a ways that are violent, humorous and poetic.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?230034</url></doc>
